                    <h2><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>Professional Summary</h2>
                    <p>Frontend Developer transitioning from logistics operations with a proven track record of 99% accuracy and process excellence at DSV Transport & Logistics. Proficient in JavaScript, React, Vue.js, and Angular through intensive ALX Africa software engineering training. Combines technical skills with real-world operational experience to build reliable, user-focused applications that solve business problems. Demonstrated ability to automate processes (40% efficiency gain), master new technologies rapidly, and deliver results in high-pressure environments. Seeking to leverage unique blend of technical expertise and operational discipline in a frontend development role.</p>
